# 读取所有数据的文件路径
def listdir(path, list_name):  # 传入存储的list
    for file in os.listdir(path):
        file_path = os.path.join(path, file)
        if os.path.isdir(file_path):
            listdir(file_path, list_name)
        else:
            list_name.append(file_path)

ZS method指标计算

计算步骤：

  • 计算每天的日均值
  • 计算相对于日均值的差值
  • 计算对应于差值结果的样本标准差
  • 计算ZS值

# 计算每天的日均值

# 15天，17行，13列的数组
data_average = np.zeros((15,17,13), dtype=float)

for i in range(15):
    for j in range(17):
        for k in range(13):
            data = []
            key = 0
            total = 0.0
            data.append(nc.Dataset(Data2015[i])['T'][0,4,:,:][j,k])
            data.append(nc.Dataset(Data2016[i])['T'][0,4,:,:][j,k])
            data.append(nc.Dataset(Data2017[i])['T'][0,4,:,:][j,k])
            data.append(nc.Dataset(Data2018[i])['T'][0,4,:,:][j,k])
            data.append(nc.Dataset(Data2019[i])['T'][0,4,:,:][j,k])
            data.append(nc.Dataset(Data2020[i])['T'][0,4,:,:][j,k])
            data.append(nc.Dataset(Data2021[i])['T'][0,4,:,:][j,k])
            data.append(nc.Dataset(Data2022[i])['T'][0,4,:,:][j,k])
            # print(data)
            for each in data:
                if math.isnan(each):
                    continue
                else:
                    total += float(each)
                    key += 1
            if key == 0:
                data_average[i,j,k] = np.nan
            else:
                data_average[i,j,k] = float(total / key)

# 计算相对于日均值的差值


# 8年，15天，17行，13列的数组
data_difference = np.zeros((8,15,17,13), dtype=float)

for i in range(15):
    for j in range(17):
        for k in range(13):
            # 2015
            data_2015 = nc.Dataset(Data2015[i])['T'][0,4,:,:][j,k]
            if math.isnan(data_2015) or math.isnan(data_average[i,j,k]):
                data_difference[0,i,j,k] = np.nan
            else:
                data_difference[0,i,j,k] = data_2015 - data_average[i,j,k]
            # 2016
            data_2016 = nc.Dataset(Data2016[i])['T'][0,4,:,:][j,k]
            if math.isnan(data_2016) or math.isnan(data_average[i,j,k]):
                data_difference[1,i,j,k] = np.nan
            else:
                data_difference[1,i,j,k] = data_2016 - data_average[i,j,k]
            # 2017
            data_2017 = nc.Dataset(Data2017[i])['T'][0,4,:,:][j,k]
            if math.isnan(data_2017) or math.isnan(data_average[i,j,k]):
                data_difference[2,i,j,k] = np.nan
            else:
                data_difference[2,i,j,k] = data_2017 - data_average[i,j,k]
            # 2018
            data_2018 = nc.Dataset(Data2018[i])['T'][0,4,:,:][j,k]
            if math.isnan(data_2018) or math.isnan(data_average[i,j,k]):
                data_difference[3,i,j,k] = np.nan
            else:
                data_difference[3,i,j,k] = data_2018 - data_average[i,j,k]
            # 2019
            data_2019 = nc.Dataset(Data2019[i])['T'][0,4,:,:][j,k]
            if math.isnan(data_2019) or math.isnan(data_average[i,j,k]):
                data_difference[4,i,j,k] = np.nan
            else:
                data_difference[4,i,j,k] = data_2019 - data_average[i,j,k]
            # 2020
            data_2020 = nc.Dataset(Data2020[i])['T'][0,4,:,:][j,k]
            if math.isnan(data_2020) or math.isnan(data_average[i,j,k]):
                data_difference[5,i,j,k] = np.nan
            else:
                data_difference[5,i,j,k] = data_2020 - data_average[i,j,k]
            # 2021
            data_2021 = nc.Dataset(Data2021[i])['T'][0,4,:,:][j,k]
            if math.isnan(data_2021) or math.isnan(data_average[i,j,k]):
                data_difference[6,i,j,k] = np.nan
            else:
                data_difference[6,i,j,k] = data_2021 - data_average[i,j,k]
            # 2022
            data_2022 = nc.Dataset(Data2022[i])['T'][0,4,:,:][j,k]
            if math.isnan(data_2022) or math.isnan(data_average[i,j,k]):
                data_difference[7,i,j,k] = np.nan
            else:
                data_difference[7,i,j,k] = data_2022 - data_average[i,j,k]

# 计算对应于差值结果的样本标准差

# 15天，17行，13列的数组
data_difference_std = np.zeros((15,17,13), dtype=float)

for i in range(15):
    for j in range(17):
        for k in range(13):
            data = []
            std = 0
            for each in data_difference[:,i,j,k]:
                if math.isnan(each):
                    continue
                else:
                    data.append(each)
            if len(data) == 0:
                std = np.nan
            else:
                std = np.std(data,ddof=1)# 求样本标准差
            data_difference_std[i,j,k] = std

# 计算ZS值

# 8年，15天，17行，13列的数组
data_ZS = np.zeros((8,15,17,13), dtype=float)

for i in range(15):
    for j in range(17):
        for k in range(13):
            # 2015
            data_2015 = nc.Dataset(Data2015[i])['T'][0,4,:,:][j,k]
            if math.isnan(data_2015):
                data_ZS[0,i,j,k] = np.nan
            else:
                data_ZS[0,i,j,k] = (data_2015 - data_average[i,j,k]) / data_difference_std[i,j,k]
            # 2016
            data_2016 = nc.Dataset(Data2016[i])['T'][0,4,:,:][j,k]
            if math.isnan(data_2016):
                data_ZS[1,i,j,k] = np.nan
            else:
                data_ZS[1,i,j,k] = (data_2016 - data_average[i,j,k]) / data_difference_std[i,j,k]
            # 2017
            data_2017 = nc.Dataset(Data2017[i])['T'][0,4,:,:][j,k]
            if math.isnan(data_2017):
                data_ZS[2,i,j,k] = np.nan
            else:
                data_ZS[2,i,j,k] = (data_2017 - data_average[i,j,k]) / data_difference_std[i,j,k]
            # 2018
            data_2018 = nc.Dataset(Data2018[i])['T'][0,4,:,:][j,k]
            if math.isnan(data_2018):
                data_ZS[3,i,j,k] = np.nan
            else:
                data_ZS[3,i,j,k] = (data_2018 - data_average[i,j,k]) / data_difference_std[i,j,k]
            # 2019
            data_2019 = nc.Dataset(Data2019[i])['T'][0,4,:,:][j,k]
            if math.isnan(data_2019):
                data_ZS[4,i,j,k] = np.nan
            else:
                data_ZS[4,i,j,k] = (data_2019 - data_average[i,j,k]) / data_difference_std[i,j,k]
            # 2020
            data_2020 = nc.Dataset(Data2020[i])['T'][0,4,:,:][j,k]
            if math.isnan(data_2020):
                data_ZS[5,i,j,k] = np.nan
            else:
                data_ZS[5,i,j,k] = (data_2020 - data_average[i,j,k]) / data_difference_std[i,j,k]
            # 2021
            data_2021 = nc.Dataset(Data2021[i])['T'][0,4,:,:][j,k]
            if math.isnan(data_2021):
                data_ZS[6,i,j,k] = np.nan
            else:
                data_ZS[6,i,j,k] = (data_2021 - data_average[i,j,k]) / data_difference_std[i,j,k]
            # 2022
            data_2022 = nc.Dataset(Data2022[i])['T'][0,4,:,:][j,k]
            if math.isnan(data_2022):
                data_ZS[7,i,j,k] = np.nan
            else:
                data_ZS[7,i,j,k] = (data_2022 - data_average[i,j,k]) / data_difference_std[i,j,k]

# 获得8年，15天的ZS数据
# 获得8年，15天的ZS热异常数据（超过指定阈值为异常）

imgData = [[0 for col in range(15)] for row in range(8)]
for i in range(8):
    data = data_ZS[i,:,:,:]
    for j in range(15):
        day_data = np.rot90(data[j],1)
        imgData[i][j] = day_data


ZS_Anomalies = [[0 for col in range(15)] for row in range(8)]
for year in range(8):
    for i in range(15):
        data_zsa = [[0 for col in range(17)] for row in range(13)]# 13行，17列，因为上面进行了90逆时针旋转
        for j in range(13):
            for k in range(17):
                if imgData[year][i][j][k] >= data_difference_std[i,k,j]*0.5:# 阈值
                    data_zsa[j][k] = imgData[year][i][j][k]
                else:
                    data_zsa[j][k] = np.nan
        ZS_Anomalies[year][i] = data_zsa

if imgData[0][1].all() == imgData[2][1].all():

else:
    print('NO')
